<h2>Help</h2>

<p>
    Welcome to the Techify Help Center! Here you can find answers to common questions and support resources.
</p>

<h3>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>How do I place an order?</strong> - You can place an order by browsing our products and adding them to your cart. Once you're ready, proceed to checkout and follow the steps to complete your purchase.</li>
    <li><strong>What payment methods do you accept?</strong> - We accept various payment methods including credit/debit cards, Bkash, and other secure payment options.</li>
    <li><strong>How can I track my order?</strong> - After placing an order, you'll receive an email with a tracking number. Use this number to track your order on our website or the courier's website.</li>
    <li><strong>What is your return policy?</strong> - We offer a 30-day return policy on most items. Please visit our Returns page for more details.</li>
    <li><strong>How do I contact customer support?</strong> - You can contact us via email at <a href="mailto:support@techify.com">support@techify.com</a> or through our Contact Us page.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Need More Help?</h3>
<p>
    If you can't find the answer you're looking for, feel free to reach out to our support team. We're here to help!
</p>